Method Detail

getConsoleText

public String getConsoleText()
Returns the string used in the console as prefix for each line to show the logging level. The console text is translated by using the message key "ConsolePreference.CONSOLE_TEXT_<LogLevel>.ConsoleText".

Returns:
console text string
